title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 23 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 23 2022
description:
Donald Trump Jr. responds to the Hunter Biden laptop story, thinks Hunter will get away with it, stresses importance of fighting to win the 2022 midterms, his new news app, MxM News, and whether he thinks Biden will run for reelection. Former Trump advisor economist Stephen Moore on how to fix inflation, save the economy. The culture wars and the midterms. C&B celebrate National Puppy Day!
